OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1781884084
OL,3,CDamaged Kendal bridge to close on
OL,4,CMonday for stone recovery as driver is
OL,5,Ccharged
OL,7,FThe historic Nether Bridge will be
OL,8,Fclosed for a time on Monday as
OL,9,Fheritage stone work is recovered from
OL,10,Fthe water.
OL,12,FAt around 1am on Wednesday 17th June,
OL,13,Fa crash damaged 10 metres of the
OL,14,Fparapet wall.
OL,16,FA man has now been charged with
OL,17,Fdangerous driving and failing to
OL,18,Fprovide a roadside breath test. He's
OL,19,Fscheduled to appear at Barrow
OL,20,FMagistrates Court on 17th August.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
