PN,32302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1781884084
OL,3,CDamaged Kendal bridge to close on
OL,4,CMonday for stone recovery as driver is
OL,5,Ccharged
OL,7,FNether Bridge is a 'Scheduled Ancient
OL,8,FMonument,' which recognises the
OL,9,Fbridge's status as a nationally
OL,10,Fimportant or historic building.
OL,12,FIt is hoped that the recovered
OL,13,Fheritage stone, which was knocked from
OL,14,Fthe parapet into the watercourse, can
OL,15,Fbe reused in the repair where possible.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1781884084
OL,3,CDamaged Kendal bridge to close on
OL,4,CMonday for stone recovery as driver is
OL,5,Ccharged
OL,7,FWestmorland and Furness Council has
OL,8,Fsaid a full road closure is required
OL,9,Fto carry out the work but in order to
OL,10,Fminimise disruption, this will be
OL,11,Fbetween 9.30am and 2pm to avoid peak
OL,12,Ftravel times.
OL,14,F"Due to the nature of the work, and
OL,15,Fthe need to position a truck-mounted
OL,16,Fcrane on the road for lifting
OL,17,Foperations, a full road closure will
OL,18,Fbe required," a spokesperson said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1781884084
OL,3,CDamaged Kendal bridge to close on
OL,4,CMonday for stone recovery as driver is
OL,5,Ccharged
OL,7,F"Traffic will therefore be diverted
OL,8,Fvia Romney Bridge and Milnthorpe Road,
OL,9,Fwith appropriate signage in place to
OL,10,Fprevent HGVs from using Parkside Road
OL,11,Fdue to the low bridge restriction.
OL,13,F"To minimise disruption, the closure
OL,14,Fwill be implemented from 9.30am to
OL,15,Favoid peak travel times and school
OL,16,Fdrop-off. The bridge will remain open
OL,17,Ffor pedestrians and cyclists
OL,18,Fthroughout.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1781884084
OL,3,CDamaged Kendal bridge to close on
OL,4,CMonday for stone recovery as driver is
OL,5,Ccharged
OL,7,F"It is expected that the work should
OL,8,Fbe completed and the bridge open again
OL,9,Fno later than 2pm."
OL,11,FThe bridge is a Scheduled Ancient
OL,12,FMonument spanning the River Kent,
OL,13,Fwhich has both Site of Special
OL,14,FScientific Interest and Special Area
OL,15,Fof Conservation environmental
OL,16,Fdesignations.
OL,18,F"Approximately 10 metres of the
OL,19,Fparapet wall has been displaced," the
OL,20,Flocal authority added.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1781884084
OL,3,CDamaged Kendal bridge to close on
OL,4,CMonday for stone recovery as driver is
OL,5,Ccharged
OL,7,F"It is too early at this stage to say
OL,8,Fwhen a permanent repair will be
OL,9,Fundertaken, but it will be a number of
OL,10,Fmonths as it will require the
OL,11,Fappointment of a contractor
OL,12,Fexperienced in such high-profile
OL,13,Fheritage work, and (depending on the
OL,14,Frequired access measures) Environment
OL,15,FAgency consent and Natural England
OL,16,FAssent.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1781884084
OL,3,CDamaged Kendal bridge to close on
OL,4,CMonday for stone recovery as driver is
OL,5,Ccharged
OL,7,FCouncillor Peter Thornton, Cabinet
OL,8,FMember for Highways and ICT, said:
OL,9,F"The team, starting with the out of
OL,10,Fhours crew who were called out to the
OL,11,Fincident, pulled out all the stops to
OL,12,Fmake safe, assess the structure, place
OL,13,Fthe concrete barriers and open the
OL,14,Froad that same morning.
OL,16,F"It is important that the stonework is
OL,17,Frecovered from the watercourse as soon
OL,18,Fas possible and I am pleased we have
OL,19,Fbeen able to work with the relevant
OL,20,Fstatutory environmental bodies to make
OL,21,Fthis happen so soon.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1781884084
OL,3,CDamaged Kendal bridge to close on
OL,4,CMonday for stone recovery as driver is
OL,5,Ccharged
OL,7,F"There will be some disruption, but we
OL,8,Faim to keep that to a minimum and I am
OL,9,Fsure that people will understand the
OL,10,Fneed to carry out this work so this
OL,11,Fimportant part of Kendal's heritage
OL,12,Fcan be repaired properly and
OL,13,Fappropriately."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
